(81, 1, '2016-06-16 22:53:57', '2016-06-16 22:53:57', '[tabs]\r\n[tab title="<strong>Yuriel Amaro</strong>"]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_83" align="alignnone" width="300"]<a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Yuri1.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="wp-image-83 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Yuri1-300x203.jpg" alt="Yuri1" width="300" height="203" /></a> Yuriel Amaro, Six Claude Cahun avec lunettes prémonitoires, 48"x32", techniques mixtes sur bois, 2015[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_84" align="alignnone" width="203"]<a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Yuri2.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="wp-image-84 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Yuri2-203x300.jpg" alt="Yuri2" width="203" height="300" /></a> Yuriel Amaro, The Heroin of the Carnival, techniques mixtes sur bois, 36" x 24", 2014[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_85" align="alignnone" width="300"]<a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Yuri3.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="wp-image-85 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Yuri3-300x213.jpg" alt="Yuri3" width="300" height="213" /></a> Yuriel Amaro, Claude Cahun en Méduse, d''après l’autoportrait de 1914, techniques mixtes sur toile, 28" x 20", 2015[/caption]\r\n\r\n[/tab]\r\n[tab title="<strong>Eloisa Aquino</strong>"]\r\n<p class="rtejustify"><strong>Eloisa Aquino, <a href="http://nomorepotlucks.org/site/claude-cahun/" target="_blank"><em>Claude Cahun</em></a>, série <em>The Life and Times of Butch Dykes</em>, vol. 2, Montréal, B&amp;D Press, 2010.</strong></p>\r\n<p class="rtejustify">« The French photographer, performer, activist and writer Claude Cahun is now considered one of the most subversive artists of European Modernism. Her portraits reveal her wicked sense of humor and her search for an identity that challenged current views on gender and sexuality.\r\nThis zine re-creates Cahun''s portraits with beautiful ink drawings and shows Cahun''s impassioned engagement with issues of identity and progressive politics. »</p>\r\n<p class="rtejustify">Pour toute information, consulter le site de <a href="http://banddpress.blogspot.ca/" target="_blank">B&amp;D Press</a>.</p>\r\n<p class="rtejustify"><a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Eloisa.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-88 size-full" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Eloisa.png" alt="Eloisa" width="439" height="613" /></a></p>\r\n[/tab]\r\n[tab title="<strong>Dehors/Audela</strong>"]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://dehorsaudela.blogspot.it/p/i-giovani-doggi-non-hanno-che-una-paura.html" target="_blank">Site de la troupe Dehors/Audela</a>\r\n\r\nVisualiser un extrait du spectacle <em>Perfetto Indefinito</em> dont la première aura lieu en juin 2016 au théâtre de la Tenuta dello Scompiglio :\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oR0dspnu-To" target="_blank"><span data-reactid=".0.1.0.0.0.0.0.1">Fragment du spectacle Perfetto Indefinito</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela1.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-90 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela1-212x300.jpg" alt="audela1" width="212" height="300" /></a> <a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela2.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-91 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela2-195x300.jpg" alt="audela2" width="195" height="300" /></a> <a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela3.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-92 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela3-300x200.jpg" alt="audela3" width="300" height="200" /></a> <a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela4.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-93 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela4-300x200.jpg" alt="audela4" width="300" height="200" /></a> <a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela5.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-94 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela5-300x205.jpg" alt="audela5" width="300" height="205" /></a> <a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela6.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-95 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela6-300x202.jpg" alt="audela6" width="300" height="202" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/tab]\r\n[/tabs]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Postérité', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'posterite', '', '', '2016-06-16 22:53:57', '2016-06-16 22:53:57', '', 0, 'http://wp.dev/?page_id=81', 0, 'page', '', 0),
