ws Cahun''s impassioned engagement with issues of identity and progressive politics. »</p>\r\n<p class="rtejustify">Pour toute information, consulter le site de <a href="http://banddpress.blogspot.ca/" target="_blank">B&amp;D Press</a>.</p>\r\n<p class="rtejustify"><a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Eloisa.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-88 size-full" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Eloisa.png" alt="Eloisa" width="439" height="613" /></a></p>\r\n[/tab]\r\n[tab title="<strong>Dehors/Audela</strong>"]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://dehorsaudela.blogspot.it/p/i-giovani-doggi-non-hanno-che-una-paura.html" target="_blank">Site de la troupe Dehors/Audela</a>\r\n\r\nVisualiser un extrait du spectacle <em>Perfetto Indefinito</em> dont la première aura lieu en juin 2016 au théâtre de la Tenuta dello Scompiglio :\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oR0dspnu-To" target="_blank"><span data-reactid=".0.1.0.0.0.0.0.1">Fragment du spectacle Perfetto Indefinito</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela1.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-90 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela1-212x300.jpg" alt="audela1" width="212" height="300" /></a> <a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela2.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-91 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela2-195x300.jpg" alt="audela2" width="195" height="300" /></a> <a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela3.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-92 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela3-300x200.jpg" alt="audela3" width="300" height="200" /></a> <a href="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela4.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-93 size-medium" src="http://wp.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/audela4-300x200.jpg" alt="audela4" width="300" height="200" /></a> <a href="http://wp.dev/wp-c